# Styling Guidelines

## CSS Architecture

### Design Tokens
All design tokens are defined in [src/lib/styles/tokens.css](mdc:src/lib/styles/tokens.css)

**Asteria Tokens:**
- `--bg`: #0C0A1A (Background)
- `--panel`: #141127 (Panel/card background)
- `--ink`: #EDEBFF (Primary text)
- `--ink-dim`: #C9C5F2 (Secondary text)
- `--muted`: #A39ED4 (Muted text)
- `--love`: #F06FA3 (Love journey)
- `--career`: #F2C14E (Career journey)
- `--destiny`: #9C6CFF (Destiny journey)
- `--clarity`: #30D5C8 (Clarity journey)
- `--glass`: rgba(255,255,255,0.06) (Glass effect)
- `--radius`: 20px (Border radius)

**Cosmo Tokens:**
- `--bg`: #0E1B2E
- `--panel`: #111E33
- `--ink`: #EAF3FF
- `--accent1`: #7CF7FF (Gradient start)
- `--accent2`: #7AA7FF (Gradient middle)
- `--accent3`: #C07CFF (Gradient end)
- `--glass`: transparent (No glass effect)
- `--radius`: 12px (Tighter radius)

### Common Components

**Cards:**
```css
.card {
  background: var(--glass);
  backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
  border: 1px solid #ffffff1f;
  border-radius: var(--radius);
}

/* Cosmo overrides automatically */
[data-brand='cosmo'] .card {
  background: #0F1C31;
  backdrop-filter: none;
  border: 1px solid #22385F;
}
```

**Buttons:**
```css
.btn {
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 8px;
  padding: 12px 16px;
  border-radius: 12px;
  border: 1px solid #ffffff22;
  background: #ffffff10;
  color: var(--ink);
  cursor: pointer;
  transition: transform .12s ease;
}

.btn:hover {
  transform: translateY(-1px);
}
```

**Typography:**
```css
.h1 { font-size: 56px; line-height: 64px; margin: 0 0 16px; }
.h3 { font-size: 28px; line-height: 36px; margin: 0 0 8px; }
.sub { opacity: .8; max-width: 560px; margin-bottom: 24px; }
```

**Layout:**
```css
.section { padding: 96px 24px; max-width: 1120px; margin: 0 auto; }
.grid { display: grid; gap: 24px; }
```

## Responsive Design

### Mobile-First Approach
Start with mobile styles, then add desktop enhancements:

```css
/* Mobile (default) */
.grid {
  grid-template-columns: 1fr;
}

/* Tablet */
@media (min-width: 768px) {
  .grid {
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
  }
}

/* Desktop */
@media (min-width: 1024px) {
  .grid {
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
  }
}
```

